### 6. UPDATE INSTAGRAM EMBED LINKS
PUT {{baseUrl}}/influencers/embed-links
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "instagram",
  "embedLinks": [
    "https://www.instagram.com/p/NEW_POST_1/embed",
    "https://www.instagram.com/p/NEW_POST_2/embed",
    "https://www.instagram.com/p/NEW_POST_3/embed"
  ]
}

### 6b. UPDATE LINKEDIN EMBED LINKS
PUT {{baseUrl}}/influencers/embed-links
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "linkedin",
  "embedLinks": [
    "https://www.linkedin.com/embed/feed/update/urn:li:activity:NEW_POST_1",
    "https://www.linkedin.com/embed/feed/update/urn:li:share:NEW_POST_2",
    "https://www.linkedin.com/embed/feed/update/urn:li:activity:NEW_POST_3"
  ]
}

### 7. GET MY PROFILE (Influencer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. BROWSE ALL INFLUENCERS (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. BROWSE INFLUENCERS BY CATEGORY (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers?category=fashion&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. BROWSE INFLUENCERS BY FOLLOWER RANGE (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers?minFollowers=100000&maxFollowers=500000&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. GET INFLUENCER BY ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/INFLUENCER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11b. GET INFLUENCER'S EMBED POSTS (Both Platforms)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/INFLUENCER_ID_HERE/embeds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11c. GET INFLUENCER'S INSTAGRAM EMBEDS ONLY
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/INFLUENCER_ID_HERE/embeds?platform=instagram
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11d. GET INFLUENCER'S LINKEDIN EMBEDS ONLY
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/INFLUENCER_ID_HERE/embeds?platform=linkedin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. VIEW INFLUENCER PROFILE (Startup - uses 1 view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/view/INFLUENCER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. MARK INTEREST IN INFLUENCER (Startup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/influencers/interest/INFLUENCER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Interested in collaboration for our new product launch"
}

### 14. GET MY INTERESTS (Startup)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/my/interests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. GET PROFILE INTERESTS (Influencer - who's interested in me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/influencers/me/interests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

